en-US.title: Mabel Wadsworth Center
en-US.description: Mabel Wadsworth Center is a feminist sexual and reproductive healthcare provider. They provide a range of services including pregnancy and abortion care, sexual and reproductive health services, cancer screenings, mental health counseling, primary care, LGBTQ+ healthcare including gender affirming hormone therapy, and various community services.

address: 700 Mt Hope Ave #420, Bangor, ME 04401, USA
